Super Bowl's Greatest Commercials 2014 

Boomer Esiason and Sarah Shahi (of Person of Interest) host a look at the best commercials to air during past Super Bowls, with viewers choosing the top spot. Sneak peeks are shown for some of the ads for 2014 and behind-the-scenes footage from this year's Volkswagen commercial. Also, the five finalists for Doritos' Crash The Super Bowl contest are briefly interviewed and their entries are shown.

This aired on CBS HD on Jan 29, 2014. The quality is something like A8 V8 since it was recorded using analog methods.
